The dense jungle continues ahead, but there's light
filtering through from deeper within. It might be connected
to somewhere else.

If we can cut down the underbrush with something like an
axe, we might be able to proceed further.
\N<Dalton>Hey, Luna-chan... Can I talk to you for a sec?

\N<Dalton>I wouldn't tell this to other adventurers, but I'll make an
exception for you, Luna-chan... Actually, if you go through
these bushes, there's a shortcut to the "4th layer".

\N<Luna>Really?! I wouldn't have noticed at all without you telling
me... That's amazing

\N<Dalton>Heh heh heh♪ It's a bit of a "tight path", but if Luna-chan
doesn't mind, I can guide you... What do you say?

It seems Dalton knows a shortcut to the "4th layer"... Will
you have him guide you?

\N<Luna>Yes, please, I'd appreciate it♪ Valuable information from a
senior adventurer is a big help.

And so, the two of them forcefully made their way step by
step through the narrow animal trail.

As they were nearing the end of the animal trail, Dalton
noticed something and stopped in his tracks.
\N<Dalton>Damn...! Luna-chan, come over here for a sec.

\N<Dalton>We're in a bit of a pickle... Do you see that? Over there is
a beast well-known among adventurers for being ferocious.
\N<Luna>Eh?! Can we handle it just the two of us...?

\N<Dalton>No, it's better not to engage. If it spots us, there's no
guarantee we'll make it out alive. Let's hide until it
passes by.

\N<Dalton>Let's wait it out in the shadow of this tree... Come on,
quickly, this way!
A reminiscence scene has been added.
Your impression of Dalton has been updated.
"1_t=7_subject=キスしちゃった、でも事故だから...ね"

\N<Luna>Although I appreciate it, I was thinking I'd like to
properly explore this floor... I think I'll take another
opportunity.

\N<Dalton>Hmm, I see... Well, that's important too, understood... But
if you change your mind, I'll guide you anytime, so feel
free to ask me again.
\N<Dalton>(To come this far and be just a little bit away...)

Dalton had a look on his face as if something had thrown off
his plans.

～Battle System Part 1～ There is an "Evasion System" that
allows you to dodge erotic attacks from enemies.

If you input the four random arrows displayed on the
keyboard within the time limit, you can evade the erotic
attack.

This is the timer that shows the time limit. If you input
the four arrows correctly before the timer runs out, you
successfully evade (be careful as it decreases faster when
in a lewd state).

This is a UI panel designed for mouse operation. You can
click directly on the arrow panel to input the random
arrows.

Lastly, there's the clothing HP <AP>. When AP reaches 0,
your clothes will be damaged, increasing the frequency of
erotic attacks from enemies. You can repair/enhance them at
the village's "\C[2]Tailor\C[0]".

For those who repeatedly select the same battle command,
"Command Memory: ON" in the options is recommended.

In the dungeon, "stairs" will "\C[2]randomly move\C[0]" each
time. It's recommended to use the item "\C[3]Compass\C[0]"
that points to the stairs.
